data.description: Charming brick home in quiet, family-friendly neighborhood of Redstone Commons. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home features 1,830 square feet of living space, built in 2019. The open-concept layout is perfect for entertaining, with a spacious living room that flows seamlessly into the kitchen and dining area. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large island with seating. The master suite is a private oasis, with a walk-in closet and a private bathroom. The backyard is perfect for relaxing and enjoying the Florida sunshine, with a large patio and a pergola.
